@scribblemaniac @matteocrippa

I think it would be nice to have a license attribute for apps. We don't necessarily have to display it in the generated README right now, but it could be useful in the future for a search filter or something like that.

It could have a limited set of values like: `apache`, `bsd`, `gpl`, `lgpl`, `mit`, `mozilla`, `cddl`, `eclipse`, `public_domain` and `other` (based off of [OSI's "Popular Licenses"](https://opensource.org/licenses))

@dkhamsing Thoughts?

